title: Initial Advice for Week 4, Players You Should Drop, and Hidden Gems on Unexpected Teams | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 309)
description:
The Ringer’s Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly offer up their locks heading into Week 4 (1:30) and list their “Thank Me Laters” for the week and players you should drop (17:00) before diving into the fantasy impact of Baker Mayfield and Josh Rosen starting next week (28:30).
